 nts at the end so join us on this all ages and abilities ride!\n\nSee belo
 w for details.\n\n* Date: Saturday\, April 25\, 2026\n* Time: 10:00 a.m. m
 eet\; 10:15 a.m. departure\n* Meeting Location: Southwest corner of Eglint
