 11km along Eglinton West Trail to Centennial Park. (https://ridewithgps.co
 m/routes/54489433) Route map (subject to change)\n\n (https://ridewithgps.
 com/routes/54489433)\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/ride_to_centennial_park
